name: Silfirum II
description:
I forget to think until I wake, a half-dream

Tangled from the starry night,
Sketching with my eyes of the night's black
To that day I am sure a long journey to this world

The day that lies before me will be a long day
The night is waiting to come
-

The great Spirit of a spirit
How many angels sing 
How many songs tell
How many voices shout
How much more you hear, //how much more I give
I sing what I sing by myself,¢¢¢
By my own voice, my words from the heavens,
By my own heart, my speech and my deeds,
By all my eyes, all my soul's
The infinite, the inexpressible,

Congrats Everyone
